  "about": {
   "description": "Sherpa is a Monte Carlo event generator for the Simulation of High-Energy\nReactions of PArticles in lepton-lepton, lepton-photon, photon-photon,\nlepton-hadron and hadron-hadron collisions. Simulation programs - also\ndubbed event generators - like Sherpa are indispensable work horses for\ncurrent particle physics phenomenology and are (at) the interface between\ntheory and experiment.\n",
   "dev_url": "https://gitlab.com/sherpa-team/sherpa",
   "doc_url": "https://sherpa-team.gitlab.io/",
   "home": "https://gitlab.com/sherpa-team/sherpa",
   "license": "GPL-3.0-or-later",
